msgid "The number of completion rows to display to the user."
msgstr "ຈຳນວນແຖວຂອງໂຕຕື່ມໂຄ້ດທີ່ຈະສະແດງໃຫ້ຜູ້ໃຊ້ເຫັນ."

#: data/gsettings/org.gnome.builder.editor.gschema.xml:134
#: src/plugins/editorui/tweaks.ui:65
