msgid "If enabled, Builder will clear build caches upon startup."
msgstr "ຖ້າເປີດໃຊ້, Builder ຈະລຶບແຄດການສ້າງຕອນເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ."

#: data/gsettings/org.gnome.builder.gschema.xml:50
