msgid ""
"If enabled, stderr of language servers will be redirected to the console."
msgstr "ຖ້າເປີດໃຊ້, stderr ຂອງ language servers ຈະຖືກສົ່ງໄປທີ່ console."

#: data/gsettings/org.gnome.builder.gschema.xml:74
